WHO RULED TOGETHER

3
00:00:13,514 --> 00:00:16,050
AND CREATED HARMONY
FOR ALL THE LAND.

4
00:00:16,084 --> 00:00:19,487
TO DO THIS, THE ELDEST
USED HER UNICORN POWERS

5
00:00:19,520 --> 00:00:21,455
TO RAISE THE SUN AT DAWN.

6
00:00:21,489 --> 00:00:25,426
THE YOUNGER BROUGHT OUT THE MOON
TO BEGIN THE NIGHT.

7
00:00:25,459 --> 00:00:27,428
THUS, THE TWO SISTERS
MAINTAINED BALANCE

8
00:00:27,461 --> 00:00:29,330
FOR THEIR KINGDOM
AND THEIR SUBJECTS --

9
00:00:29,363 --> 00:00:31,632
