HER ELDER SISTER BROUGHT FORTH

13
00:00:39,540 --> 00:00:43,377
BUT SHUNNED AND SLEPT
THROUGH HER BEAUTIFUL NIGHT.

14
00:00:43,411 --> 00:00:45,679
ONE FATEFUL DAY,
THE YOUNGER UNICORN

15
00:00:45,713 --> 00:00:49,083
REFUSED TO LOWER THE MOON
TO MAKE WAY FOR THE DAWN.

16
00:00:49,117 --> 00:00:51,385
THE ELDER SISTER
TRIED TO REASON WITH HER,

17
00:00:51,419 --> 00:00:54,088
BUT THE BITTERNESS
IN THE YOUNG ONE'S HEART

18
00:00:54,122 --> 00:00:56,690
HAD TRANSFORMED HER INTO
A WICKED MARE OF DARKNESS --

19
00:00:56,724 --> 00:00:58,192
NIGHTMARE MOON.

20
00:00:58,226 --> 00:00:59,393
[ THUNDER CRASHES ]

21
00:00:59,427 --> 00:01:03,531
SHE VOWED THAT SHE WOULD SHROUD
THE LAND IN ETERNAL NIGHT.

22
00:01:03,564 --> 00:01:05,799
RELUCTANTLY, THE ELDER SISTER

23
00:01:05,833 --> 00:01:09,137
HARNESSED THE MOST POWERFUL
MAGIC KNOWN TO PONYDOM --

24
00:01:09,137 --> 00:01:11,739
THE ELEMENTS OF HARMONY.

25
00:01:11,772 --> 00:01:14,342
USING THE MAGIC
OF THE ELEMENTS OF HARMONY,

26
00:01:14,375 --> 00:01:16,144
SHE DEFEATED HER YOUNGER SISTER

27
00:01:16,144 --> 00:01:20,248
AND BANISHED HER PERMANENTLY
ON THE MOON.

28
